  "text": "Before the establishment of CNODES, the Institute for Clinical Evaluative Sciences (ICES) created the Vaccine and Immunization Surveillance in Ontario (VISION) as a vaccine vigilance system. The ICES is a healthcare and health services research institute in Ontario, and also houses Ontario's healthcare claims data [CITATION_1] .",
